I've found over the years the same thing, different dizzy for different
applications. The trike and baja's get .009 and the truck 1641 vacilates
between a 205T and a SVGA, SVGA winning out. My old 71 bug had a 1600
dual point .050/34 PICT-3 and the 72 bug that I did long distance in had
a 1600 .019/34 PICT-3 and 1.25:1 rockers.

Ray in Kent WA
67 SC 1641 34 PICT-3
71 Trike 1835 Holly 5200 progressive
Volks Air 1584 28 PICT-1

